      <taskDescription>&lt;strong&gt;Aufgabenstellung:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&#xd;
&lt;br /&gt;&#xd;
Gegeben ist folgende Verteilungsfunktion: $F(x)= \begin{cases} 0 &amp;amp; \mbox{f&amp;uuml;r }\quad x &amp;lt; [var=$A] \\ [var=$AWsk1] &amp;amp; \mbox{f&amp;uuml;r }\quad [var=$A] \le x &amp;lt; [var=$B] \\ [var=$AWsk2k] &amp;amp; \mbox{f&amp;uuml;r }\quad [var=$B] \le x &amp;lt; [var=$C] \\ [var=$AWsk3k] &amp;amp; \mbox{f&amp;uuml;r }\quad [var=$C] \le x &amp;lt; [var=$D] \\ [var=$AWsk4k] &amp;amp; \mbox{f&amp;uuml;r }\quad [var=$D] \le x &amp;lt; [var=$Ee] \\ 1 &amp;amp; \mbox{f&amp;uuml;r }\quad [var=$Ee] \le x \end{cases}$&lt;br /&gt;&#xd;
&lt;br /&gt;&#xd;
Wie lautet die Wahrscheinlichkeitsfunktion?&lt;br /&gt;&#xd;
&lt;br /&gt;&#xd;
&lt;strong&gt;Einreichung:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&#xd;
&lt;br /&gt;&#xd;
$\enspace \, x_i \, \enspace$ &amp;nbsp;&lt;input name=&quot;field1&quot; size=&quot;6&quot; type=&quot;text&quot; value=&quot;field1&quot; /&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;input name=&quot;field2&quot; size=&quot;6&quot; type=&quot;text&quot; value=&quot;field2&quot; /&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;input name=&quot;field3&quot; size=&quot;6&quot; type=&quot;text&quot; value=&quot;field3&quot; /&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;input name=&quot;field4&quot; size=&quot;6&quot; type=&quot;text&quot; value=&quot;field4&quot; /&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;input name=&quot;field5&quot; size=&quot;6&quot; type=&quot;text&quot; value=&quot;field5&quot; /&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;&#xd;
&lt;br /&gt;&#xd;
$f(x_i)$ &amp;nbsp;&lt;input name=&quot;field6&quot; size=&quot;6&quot; type=&quot;text&quot; value=&quot;field6&quot; /&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;input name=&quot;field7&quot; size=&quot;6&quot; type=&quot;text&quot; value=&quot;field7&quot; /&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;input name=&quot;field8&quot; size=&quot;6&quot; type=&quot;text&quot; value=&quot;field8&quot; /&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;input name=&quot;field9&quot; size=&quot;6&quot; type=&quot;text&quot; value=&quot;field9&quot; /&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;input name=&quot;field10&quot; size=&quot;6&quot; type=&quot;text&quot; value=&quot;field10&quot; /&gt;&amp;nbsp;&#xd;
